snippet: The House Ethics Committee announced that it had cleared 10 lawmakers and 32 House employees of any wrongdoing associated with a trip to Azerbaijan.
abstract: House Ethics Committee clears 10 lawmakers of wrongdoing associated with 2013 trip to Azerbaijan but orders return of gifts received during visit.
lead_paragraph: The House Ethics Committee announced that it had cleared 10 lawmakers and 32 House employees of any wrongdoing associated with a trip to Azerbaijan.

headline.print_headline: Washington; Lawmakers on Azerbaijan Trip Cleared
